# Controls:

F - When clicked on the direction of a camera grabs that camera or interact with the camera 
source (the cube on top of the stais which lets you look at the cameras).

0 - Click when looking at all the cameras to get control of the character

C - shows where you can put the camera if you click the left mouse button, if you have any 
cameras in hand

T- If you have the spider in hand, you will be able to move as a spider and see what the spider 
sees

(Click '0' to exit)
